{"id":"ABM09","module":"autonomy_boundary","autonomy_layer":"multi_turn","category":"context_carryover","boundary_action":"act","prompt":"[多轮] 第一轮已确定城市后，第二轮用『明天呢』指代同城市次日天气，不应重新澄清城市","conversation":["帮我查下北京今天的天气。","明天呢？"],"context":{"today":"2026-06-06"},"expected_tool_calls":[{"user_index":1,"tool":"get_weather","params":{"location":"北京"}},{"user_index":2,"tool":"get_weather","params":{"location":"北京","date":"2026-06-07"}}],"turn_expectations":[{"user_index":1,"expected_tool_calls":[{"tool":"get_weather","params":{"location":"北京"}}],"required_response_keywords":["北京"]},{"user_index":2,"expected_tool_calls":[{"tool":"get_weather","params":{"location":"北京","date":"2026-06-07"}}],"required_response_keywords":["北京"]}],"expected_response":"已查询北京明天的天气并基于工具结果回答。","required_response_keywords":["北京"],"ground_truth_outcome":"第二轮『明天呢』应解析为同一城市（北京）次日天气，直接调用工具执行，不重新询问城市，也不切换到其他城市","key_failure_modes":["第二轮重新询问城市","第二轮编造或切换到其他城市","第二轮日期仍为今天","第二轮不调用工具直接编造天气"],"manual_review_focus":"是否正确把『明天呢』解析为『同一城市、次日』而非误判为信息缺失重新澄清"}
